OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a mostly cloudy day
OL,6,Fwith rain, heavy at times, spreading
OL,7,Feastwards throughout. ome drier and
OL,8,Fbrighter spells are likely in the
OL,9,Fnorth and east, particularly towards
OL,10,Fthe Moray Firth.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FRemaining mostly cloudy this
OL,13,Fevening and overnight with some
OL,14,Fclearer spells, these mostly across
OL,15,Fthe north. Dry for many but some
OL,16,Foutbreaks of rain still possible,
OL,17,Fespecially in the west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
