OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FLargely dry start with bright
OL,6,Fspells in the north and east. Through
OL,7,Fthe morning, cloud and rain will
OL,8,Fspread east. Rain heavy and persistent
OL,9,Fat times, especially in the west.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMostly
OL,12,Fcloudy and breezy few days with spells
OL,13,Fof rain spreading eastwards. Rain may
OL,14,Fbe heavy an17d persistent in the west
OL,15,Fwith the best of any brighter spells
OL,16,Fin east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
